# Hand-collected source images dropped here for the import-local-icons
# script to consume. The script normalizes them into public/icons/, which
# is what the app actually serves and git tracks. The originals stay local
# as backups but aren't committed.
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.webp
*.gif
*.tif
*.tiff

# The catalog itself IS committed — it carries all icon metadata.
!catalog.json
